Author: catunicornmermaid
Text: No, hon. There’s absolutely nothing wrong with you. Because I want you here. So do all of us, and your friends and your family. Not having someone romantically pursuing you doesn’t change your worth in any way or detract from how beautifully YOU, you are. I know how cheesy that sounds, and how hard it is to believe. But I swear on my entire existence that it’s true. ♥️
